      public HistoricProcessInstanceQuery endOr()
      Description copied from interface: HistoricProcessInstanceQuery

      endOr() terminates an OR query on which an arbitrary amount of filter criteria were applied. To terminate the OR query which has been started by invoking HistoricProcessInstanceQuery.or(), endOr() must be invoked. Filter criteria which are applied after calling endOr() are linked together by an AND expression.

      Specified by:
